// =========================================================================
// Network Standard Library
//
// Pustaka standard untuk rangkaian deterministik.
// Semua operasi rangkaian melalui Reactor — tiada raw socket access.
//
// Prinsip: "Gate = SIAPA, Door = BAGAIMANA, Service = APA"
// =========================================================================

// ─── Service Declaration ───
// Contoh deklarasi servis dalam kod Logicodex:
//
// service WebServer {
//     port: 443,
//     requires: Net.Admin,
//     handler: WebHandler,
//     policy: Block,
// }

// ─── Connection Lifecycle ───
// Koneksi diuruskan sepenuhnya oleh Reactor (RAII auto-cleanup):
//
//   1. Reactor.accept() → Connection baru (fd assigned)
//   2. Reactor.process_event(Readable) → Connection.read()
//   3. Reactor.process_event(Writable) → Connection.write()
//   4. Connection.drop() → close(fd) deterministik
//
// Tiada manual close() — compiler akan pastikan fd ditutup.

// ─── Backpressure Policies ───
//
// policy: Block      → Tunggu buffer kosong (selamat, latency tinggi)
// policy: DropOldest → Buang data lama (real-time, boleh kehilangan data)
// policy: Error      → Kembalikan error (protocol retry, paling reliable)

// ─── Taint State Machine ───
//
//   Healthy     → Normal operation
//   Suspicious  → Pattern anomali detected (monitoring ketat)
//   Closing     → Akan di-drop (deterministic cleanup)
//
// Transition:
//   Healthy + 3 consecutive errors → Suspicious
//   Suspicious + timeout/2 → Closing
//   Suspicious + normal traffic → Healthy (recovery)
//   Hangup/Error → Closing (immediate)

// ─── Gate Requirements untuk Servis ───
//
// Servis yang listen pada port < 1024 MESTI ada requires gate.
// Contoh:
//   port: 443 → requires: Net.Admin     (HTTPS — privileged)
//   port: 80  → requires: Net.Admin     (HTTP — privileged)
//   port: 8080 → (no requires needed)   (User port)
